## Langkah 9: Commit dan Push ke GitHub

### 9.1. Setup Git dan Commit
```bash
# Initialize git (jika belum)
git init

# Add semua file
git add .

# Commit perubahan
git commit -m "Initial commit: ARSITEK Token implementation with complete tokenomics"

# Set remote origin
git remote add origin https://github.com/your-username/ARSITEK-Token.git

# Push ke main branch
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main